<h4>Quiz Complete!</h4>
<p>You answered <span class="quiz-score">0</span> out of 5 questions correctly.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 15px;">Remember: Recognising bias is a skill that improves with practice. The more you look for these patterns in everyday situations, the better you will become at spotting and addressing them.</p>
</div>

